  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/34ba1b60da928aa8e8798b72e61ff98c.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/34ba1b60da928aa8e8798b72e61ff98c.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/34ba1b60da928aa8e8798b72e61ff98c.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >From Developer</h2>Brutal top-down loot shooter. Similar games can be counted on one hand, as action games typically fall into the first-person or third-person perspective genres. <br><br>I tried to make something similar to The Division, Warframe or Destiny but on a smaller scale and from a top-down perspective, I played this game for hundreds of hours so that affected the development process :)<br><br>My game encourages an aggressive and push-forward playstyle, allowing you to combine various techniques and create impressive equipment-based combos. <br><br>Everyone can create their own build, whether it’s close combat, skills, or long-range sniping. If you enjoy top-down action games with diverse loot, then CyberCorp is exactly what you need.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b58339caa1327c7e9d4cfd8131d980f2.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b58339caa1327c7e9d4cfd8131d980f2.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b58339caa1327c7e9d4cfd8131d980f2.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are a CyberCorp fighter. In your hands lies a unique and dangerous technology - the Synth, a remotely controlled combat shell.<br>Are you ready to take your weapon and return order to the streets of the city?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flexible progression system</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/910f3c08872be2e8c9d9e126b139963f.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/910f3c08872be2e8c9d9e126b139963f.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/910f3c08872be2e8c9d9e126b139963f.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade your equipment using a card-based system of weapon and armor enhancements. Build and customize to match your playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/f1fc509ac829d3a086ce0b995aaae391.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/f1fc509ac829d3a086ce0b995aaae391.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/f1fc509ac829d3a086ce0b995aaae391.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play story and side missions with friends or random players. Equip smart and make builds for multiplayer combos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slums, factories, laboratories, elite residential complex</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b8580d5f35128c3059d0ccffef10148a.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b8580d5f35128c3059d0ccffef10148a.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b8580d5f35128c3059d0ccffef10148a.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Complete missions in various locations, explore the city of the future. Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of cyberpunk.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast paced gameplay</h2>Defend objects, hack security systems, capture control points, and uncover hidden items.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot shooter</h2>Choose your difficulty level and get the rewards. There's something for those who seek a more casual experience or a hardcore challenge.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural level generation</h2>Map, enemies, loot, encounters, weather, boss, reward are all randomized each run.<br><br>Music in some trailers by Mokka & Infraction.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/34ba1b60da928aa8e8798b72e61ff98c.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/34ba1b60da928aa8e8798b72e61ff98c.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/34ba1b60da928aa8e8798b72e61ff98c.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >From Developer</h2>Brutal top-down loot shooter. Similar games can be counted on one hand, as action games typically fall into the first-person or third-person perspective genres. <br><br>I tried to make something similar to The Division, Warframe or Destiny but on a smaller scale and from a top-down perspective, I played this game for hundreds of hours so that affected the development process :)<br><br>My game encourages an aggressive and push-forward playstyle, allowing you to combine various techniques and create impressive equipment-based combos. <br><br>Everyone can create their own build, whether it’s close combat, skills, or long-range sniping. If you enjoy top-down action games with diverse loot, then CyberCorp is exactly what you need.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b58339caa1327c7e9d4cfd8131d980f2.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b58339caa1327c7e9d4cfd8131d980f2.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b58339caa1327c7e9d4cfd8131d980f2.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are a CyberCorp fighter. In your hands lies a unique and dangerous technology - the Synth, a remotely controlled combat shell.<br>Are you ready to take your weapon and return order to the streets of the city?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flexible progression system</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/910f3c08872be2e8c9d9e126b139963f.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/910f3c08872be2e8c9d9e126b139963f.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/910f3c08872be2e8c9d9e126b139963f.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade your equipment using a card-based system of weapon and armor enhancements. Build and customize to match your playstyle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/f1fc509ac829d3a086ce0b995aaae391.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/f1fc509ac829d3a086ce0b995aaae391.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/f1fc509ac829d3a086ce0b995aaae391.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Play story and side missions with friends or random players. Equip smart and make builds for multiplayer combos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slums, factories, laboratories, elite residential complex</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b8580d5f35128c3059d0ccffef10148a.poster.avif?t=1771859689\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b8580d5f35128c3059d0ccffef10148a.webm?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116170/extras/b8580d5f35128c3059d0ccffef10148a.mp4?t=1771859689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Complete missions in various locations, explore the city of the future. Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of cyberpunk.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast paced gameplay</h2>Defend objects, hack security systems, capture control points, and uncover hidden items.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot shooter</h2>Choose your difficulty level and get the rewards. There's something for those who seek a more casual experience or a hardcore challenge.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural level generation</h2>Map, enemies, loot, encounters, weather, boss, reward are all randomized each run.<br><br>Music in some trailers by Mokka & Infraction.",
